ft-0 top-0 mr-1.5 h-8 overflow-hidden mt-1"><button class="" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-1"><span>Thought for 16 seconds</span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M5.29289 9.29289C5.68342 8.90237 6.31658 8.90237 6.70711 9.29289L12 14.5858L17.2929 9.29289C17.6834 8.90237 18.3166 8.90237 18.7071 9.29289C19.0976 9.68342 19.0976 10.3166 18.7071 10.7071L12.7071 16.7071C12.5196 16.8946 12.2652 17 12 17C11.7348 17 11.4804 16.8946 11.2929 16.7071L5.29289 10.7071C4.90237 10.3166 4.90237 9.68342 5.29289 9.29289Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></button></div></p><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="34bf3a45-28c7-4bf1-8d86-ac612101de2f" dir="auto" class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light"><p>Certainly! I'd be happy to guide you through creating a web application using Nette v3.3.0, a popular PHP framework for building robust and secure web applications.</p><h2>Prerequisites</h2><p>Before we begin, ensure you have the following installed:</p><ul><li><strong>PHP 7.2 or higher</strong></li><li><strong>Composer</strong> (Dependency Manager for PHP)</li><li><strong>Web Server</strong> (Apache, Nginx, or PHP's built-in server)</li></ul><h2>Step 1: Install Nette via Composer</h2><p>Open your terminal and navigate to the directory where you want to create your project. Run the following command to create a new Nette project:</p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-bash">composer create-project nette/web-project my-project <span class="hljs-string">"3.3.0"</span>
</code></div></div></pre><p>This command will create a new directory called <code>my-project</code> with Nette v3.3.0 installed.</p><h2>Step 2: Navigate to Your Project Directory</h2><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> my-project
</code></div></div></pre><h2>Step 3: Run the Development Server</h2><p>For development purposes, you can use PHP's built-in server:</p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-bash">php -S localhost:8000 -t www
</code></div></div></pre><p>Now, open your browser and navigate to <code>http://localhost:8000</code>. You should see the default Nette welcome page.</p><h2>Step 4: Understanding the Project Structure</h2><ul><li><strong>app/</strong>: Contains your application logic (presenters, templates, components).</li><li><strong>www/</strong>: Publicly accessible files (entry point is <code>index.php</code>).</li><li><strong>vendor/</strong>: Composer dependencies.</li><li><strong>config/</strong>: Configuration files.</li><li><strong>log/</strong>: Log files.</li><li><strong>temp/</strong>: Temporary files (cache).</li></ul><h2>Step 5: Creating a New Presenter</h2><p>Presenters handle incoming requests and generate responses. Let's create a new presenter called <code>ArticlePresenter</code>.</p><p>Create a file <code>app/Presenters/ArticlePresenter.php</code>:</p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">php</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">declare</span>(strict_types=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);

<span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">App</span>\<span class="hljs-title class_">Presenters</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">ArticlePresenter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Application</span>\<span class="hljs-title">UI</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Presenter</span>
</span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">renderDefault</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>): <span class="hljs-title">void</span>
    </span>{
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;template-&gt;articles = [
            [<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'First Article'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'content'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'Content of the first article.'</span>],
            [<span class="hljs-string">'title'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'Second Article'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'content'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">'Content of the second article.'</span>],
        ];
    }
}
</code></div></div></pre><h2>Step 6: Creating a Template</h2><p>Create a template file <code>app/Presenters/templates/Article/default.latte</code>:</p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">latte</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-latte">{block content}
&lt;h1&gt;Articles&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    {foreach $articles as $article}
        &lt;li&gt;
            &lt;h2&gt;{$article['title']}&lt;/h2&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;{$article['content']}&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/li&gt;
    {/foreach}
&lt;/ul&gt;
{/block}
</code></div></div></pre><h2>Step 7: Configuring the Router</h2><p>Modify <code>app/Router/RouterFactory.php</code> to add a route for your new presenter:</p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">php</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">declare</span>(strict_types=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);

<span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">App</span>\<span class="hljs-title class_">Router</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Application</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Routers</span>\<span class="hljs-title">RouteList</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Routing</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Router</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">RouterFactory</span>
</span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">static</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">createRouter</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>): <span class="hljs-title">Router</span>
    </span>{
        <span class="hljs-variable">$router</span> = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">RouteList</span>;

        <span class="hljs-variable">$router</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addRoute</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'articles'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Article:default'</span>);
        <span class="hljs-variable">$router</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addRoute</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'&lt;presenter&gt;/&lt;action&gt;[/&lt;id&gt;]'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Homepage:default'</span>);

        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$router</span>;
    }
}
