ere's what we'll cover:</p><ol><li><strong>Create or Update the Presenter</strong></li><li><strong>Build the Contact Form with Nette Forms</strong></li><li><strong>Handle Form Submission and Send Email</strong></li><li><strong>Modify the Template to Render the Form</strong></li><li><strong>Configure Email Sending Settings</strong></li><li><strong>Enhance Security and Validation</strong></li><li><strong>Test the Contact Form</strong></li></ol><hr><h2><strong>Step 1: Create or Update the Presenter</strong></h2><p>We need a presenter to handle the contact page logic.</p><p><strong>Create <code>ContactPresenter.php</code> in <code>app/Presenters/</code>:</strong></p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">php</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span>

<span class="hljs-keyword">declare</span>(strict_types=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);

<span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">App</span>\<span class="hljs-title class_">Presenters</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Application</span>\<span class="hljs-title">UI</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Form</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Mail</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Message</span>;
<span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Mail</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Mailer</span>;

<span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">ContactPresenter</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">Nette</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Application</span>\<span class="hljs-title">UI</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Presenter</span>
</span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Mailer <span class="hljs-variable">$mailer</span>;

    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">__construct</span>(<span class="hljs-params">Mailer <span class="hljs-variable">$mailer</span></span>)
    </span>{
        <span class="hljs-built_in">parent</span>::<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">__construct</span>();
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;mailer = <span class="hljs-variable">$mailer</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">createComponentContactForm</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>): <span class="hljs-title">Form</span>
    </span>{
        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span> = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Form</span>;

        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addText</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'name'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Jméno:'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setRequired</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Prosím, zadejte své jméno.'</span>);

        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addEmail</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'email'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Email:'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setRequired</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Prosím, zadejte svůj email.'</span>);

        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addTextArea</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'message'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Zpráva:'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setRequired</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Prosím, napište zprávu.'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addRule</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>::<span class="hljs-variable constant_">MAX_LENGTH</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Zpráva je příliš dlouhá (max 1000 znaků).'</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>);

        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addSubmit</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'send'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'Odeslat'</span>);

        <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>-&gt;onSuccess[] = [<span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'contactFormSucceeded'</span>];

        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>;
    }

    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">contactFormSucceeded</span>(<span class="hljs-params">Form <span class="hljs-variable">$form</span>, \<span class="hljs-built_in">stdClass</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$values</span></span>): <span class="hljs-title">void</span>
    </span>{
        <span class="hljs-variable">$mail</span> = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Message</span>;
        <span class="hljs-variable">$mail</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setFrom</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$values</span>-&gt;email, <span class="hljs-variable">$values</span>-&gt;name)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">addTo</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'test@gmail.com'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setSubject</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Nová zpráva z kontaktního formuláře'</span>)
            -&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">setBody</span>(
                <span class="hljs-string">"Jméno: <span class="hljs-subst">{$values-&gt;name}</span>\n"</span> .
                <span class="hljs-string">"Email: <span class="hljs-subst">{$values-&gt;email}</span>\n\n"</span> .
                <span class="hljs-string">"<span class="hljs-subst">{$values-&gt;message}</span>"</span>
            );

        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> {
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;mailer-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">send</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$mail</span>);
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">flashMessage</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Děkujeme za vaši zprávu. Brzy se vám ozveme.'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'success'</span>);
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">redirect</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'this'</span>);
        } <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (\<span class="hljs-built_in">Exception</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$e</span>) {
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">flashMessage</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'Odeslání zprávy se nezdařilo. Zkuste to prosím znovu později.'</span>, <span class="hljs-string">'error'</span>);
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">redirect</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'this'</span>);
        }
    }
}
</code></div></div></pre><p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Dependency Injection:</strong> We inject <code>Mailer</code> into the presenter to handle email sending.</li><li><strong>Form Creation:</strong> The <code>createComponentContactForm</code> method builds the form.</li><li><strong>Validation:</strong> Fields are required, and message length is limited.</li><li><strong>Form Handling:</strong> The <code>contactFormSucceeded</code> method processes the form data and sends the email.</li><li><strong>Exception Handling:</strong> Catches errors during email sending and provides user feedback.</li></ul><hr><h2><strong>Step 2: Build the Contact Form with Nette Forms</strong></h2><p>We've already created the form in the presenter. Let's ensure it's properly set up:</p><ul><li><strong>Fields:</strong><ul><li><code>name</code> (text input)</li><li><code>email</code> (email input)</li><li><code>message</code> (textarea)</li></ul></li><li><strong>Validation:</strong><ul><li>All fields are required.</li><li>Message length is limited to 1000 characters.</li></ul></li></ul><hr><h2><strong>Step 3: Handle Form Submission and Send Email</strong></h2><p>In the <code>contactFormSucceeded</code> method:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Create the Email Message:</strong></p><ul><li>Sender: User's email and name.</li><li>Recipient: <code>test@gmail.com</code>.</li><li>Subject: "Nová zpráva z kontaktního formuláře" (New message from contact form).</li><li>Body: Includes the user's name, email, and message.</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Send the Email:</strong></p><ul><li>Uses the injected <code>Mailer</code> service.</li><li>Catches exceptions to handle errors gracefully.</li></ul></li></ul><hr><h2><strong>Step 4: Modify the Template to Render the Form</strong></h2><p>Update your Latte template to render the form.</p><p><strong>Modify <code>app/Presenters/templates/Contact/default.latte</code>:</strong></p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">latte</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-latte">{block content}
