</code></div></div></pre><hr><h2><strong>2. Database Design</strong></h2><h3><strong>Step 1: Define the Database Schema</strong></h3><p>We'll need the following tables:</p><ol><li><p><strong>Users</strong></p><ul><li><code>id</code> (Primary Key)</li><li><code>username</code></li><li><code>password</code> (hashed)</li><li><code>role</code> (e.g., 'user', 'admin')</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Tools</strong></p><ul><li><code>id</code> (Primary Key)</li><li><code>name</code></li><li><code>quantity</code></li><li><code>description</code></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>BorrowedTools</strong></p><ul><li><code>id</code> (Primary Key)</li><li><code>user_id</code> (Foreign Key to Users)</li><li><code>tool_id</code> (Foreign Key to Tools)</li><li><code>quantity</code></li><li><code>borrowed_at</code> (Timestamp)</li><li><code>purpose</code> (Description provided by the user)</li><li><code>status</code> (e.g., 'borrowed', 'returned', 'lost', 'damaged', 'consumed')</li><li><code>condition</code> (Condition upon return)</li></ul></li></ol><h3><strong>Step 2: Create the Database</strong></h3><p>Create a new database named <code>tool_repository</code>.</p><h3><strong>Step 3: Create the Tables</strong></h3><p>Use the following SQL scripts to create tables:</p><p><strong>Users Table:</strong></p><pre class="!overflow-visible"><div class="dark bg-gray-950 contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md h-9">sql</div><div class="sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]"><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center"><div class="flex items-center rounded bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center py-1"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> users (
    id <span class="hljs-type">INT</span> AUTO_INCREMENT <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY,
